# License Information

## Original Work
This repository is a fork of the AWS Containers Retail Sample Application.

**Original Repository**: https://github.com/aws-containers/retail-store-sample-app  
**Original Copyright**: Amazon.com, Inc. or its affiliates. All Rights Reserved.

## Fork Purpose
This fork has been created for **educational and learning purposes only**. The modifications include:
- CloudFormation templates for VPC and EKS management infrastructure
- Regional configuration updates for ap-south-1 (Asia Pacific - Mumbai)
- Documentation updates for deployment in different AWS regions
- Additional infrastructure automation scripts

