## Educational Use Disclaimer
**This project is intended for educational purposes only and not for production use.**

The modifications and additions to this fork are provided for learning AWS container
services, infrastructure as code, and cloud architecture patterns. Users should:

- Review and understand all code before deployment
- Follow AWS security best practices
- Monitor AWS costs during experimentation
- Clean up resources after learning exercises
- Refer to official AWS documentation for production deployments

## Attribution
When using this educational fork, please maintain attribution to:
1. Original AWS Containers team for the base application
2. This educational fork for infrastructure modifications

## Support
This is an educational fork. For issues with the original application, refer to the
original AWS repository. For infrastructure-specific questions related to this fork,
please use the Issues section of this repository.
